				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Whoever says a Bard cannot solo is wrong.  A bard has levels where he/she must group inorder to speed things up.  However, there are points in your lvling that you will have more power than others.  For instance, at level 38, I could take two Hill giants at a time.  Tell me another class that can do that safely(enchanters must either have SOW or J-Boot equivalent).  And we never usually have problems getting into groups, we can do everything but are masters of nothing.  Meleers love our haste song and Casters love our clarity song.  <BR>
<BR>
Level 8 is hardly a good place to judge a class.  <BR>
